Key Match Events: Damian Lillard led the Bucks with 26 points in the victory.
Victor Wembanyama had 10 points, 10 rebounds, and three blocks in one of his worst performances of the season.
Post-Match Reflections: Damian Lillard expressed that Victor Wembanyama is 'more different' than any player he has played against in the NBA.
Lillard noted Wembanyama's ability to change or block shots as a significant factor during the game.
